                                 <date calendar="ethiopian" when="1884" when-custom="1892" evidence="internal">30 Sane 1884 E.C. (= 6 July 1892 A.D.)</date> and it mentions <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8668SebhatA">rās Sǝbḥāt</persName>
